Name: repoze.bfg.htmlpage
Version: 0.3
Summary: Dynamic HTML pages for repoze.bfg
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: UNKNOWN
Author-email: UNKNOWN
License: ZPL 2.1
Description: Overview
        ========
        
        This package provides a page-level rendering system for the
        ``repoze.bfg`` web framework.
        
        It uses familiar technologies like HTML and CSS to dynamically use an
        existing HTML document as template.
        
        Consult the documentation for ``chameleon.html`` for information on
        how to write templates.
        
        
        Credits
        -------
        
        This package was created by Malte Borch <mborch@gmail.com>, Stefan
        Eletzhofer <stefan.eletzhofer@inquant.de> and Christof Haemmerle
        <reco@nex9.com>.
        
        
        
